reviews.review_text:
First Wheel? Historical Note:

Unless I missed something this marks the first live performance by the band of The Wheel (I could have missed one somewhere).

Nice Sound mix.

Of course, this track lacks the high fine guitar licks of the Garcia album version that soar into the cosmos leaving the listener breathless. But nice vocals. Donna rarely sounds this on key.

Pretty Good.... Sounded like a good show....but then i streamed it over the PA system of the Gymnasium that i work at....not so hot.

So, unless you want a bunch of cardio crazed moms and muscley-duochebags mad at you, keep it to the car cd player...
Re: First wheel It is the first wheel, and it is also the first Samson and Delilah.
a sweet and mellow help on the way>slipnot -
